<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to RSOLV</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .logo img {
        max-width: 200px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2563EB;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .steps {
        background-color: #F3F4F6;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .steps h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #2563EB;
      }
      .steps ol {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .steps li {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .code {
        background-color: #E5E7EB;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-family: monospace;
        overflow-x: auto;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .cta {
        background-color: #2563EB;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: inline-block;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6B7280;
        border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        padding-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://rsolv.dev/images/rsolv_logo_transparent.png" alt="RSOLV Logo" />
    </div>

    <h1>Welcome to RSOLV, {@first_name}!</h1>

    <p>
      Thanks for trying RSOLV! You're just a few minutes away from automated security scanning and vulnerability remediation for your repositories.
    </p>

    <div class="steps">
      <h2>Here's how to get started:</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Enable RSOLV for your repository</strong>
          <p>
            Visit your dashboard and connect the repositories you want RSOLV to scan for security vulnerabilities.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Install our GitHub Action for automated fixes</strong>
          <div class="code">
            name: RSOLV Security Fixes<br /> on:<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;issues:<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;types: [labeled]<br /><br /> jobs:<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;security-fix:<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;runs-on: ubuntu-latest<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if: contains(github.event.issue.labels.*.name, 'rsolv:automate')<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;steps:<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- uses: rsolv-dev/rsolv-action@v1<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;with:<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;github-token: ${"{{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}"}<br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rsolv-api-key: ${"{{ secrets.RSOLV_API_KEY }}"}
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Set up your API key</strong>
          <p>Add your RSOLV API key as a repository secret:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Name: <code>RSOLV_API_KEY</code></li>
            <li>Value: <em>Find this in your dashboard at rsolv.dev/dashboard</em></li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Review your first security scan</strong>
          <p>
            RSOLV will automatically scan your repository and create issues for any vulnerabilities found. Tag issues with "rsolv:automate" to generate fix PRs!
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <p>Need help? Just reply to this email and I'll personally assist you.</p>

    <p>
      Your free trial includes 10 automated security fixes - no credit card required. RSOLV will begin scanning your repositories immediately after setup.
    </p>

    <a href="https://rsolv.dev/docs/getting-started" class="cta">View Full Documentation</a>

    <p>Best,<br />The RSOLV Team</p>

    <p>
      <strong>P.S.</strong>
      Here's a <a href="https://rsolv.dev/docs/video-tutorial">2-minute video walkthrough</a>
      if you prefer visual instructions.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        This email was sent to {@email}. If you did not sign up for RSOLV, please disregard this email.
      </p>
      <p>Â© 2025 RSOLV - Proactive Security Scanning & Automated Remediation</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
